      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "when they first sighted the object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "\"flying very fast and very high.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "At first, she said, it looked like an",
