      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "Laws of Eyesight Clarify",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "Reports of Flying Saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "By HOWARD W. BLAKESLEE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "Associated Press Science Editor",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "New York, N. Y. - The flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "saucers may be explained by cer-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "tain laws of eyesight.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "All objects appear round or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "nearly so at any distance close to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "the limit of how far a person can",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "see.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "If the objects are seen by re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "flected light, as in most cases re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "ported, they are almost certain to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "be round, and if the reflections",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "are sunlight then the sizes report-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "ed are those which would be ex-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "pected from distant light reflec-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "tions.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "Descriptions of virtually all the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "saucers as round and flat fit ex-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "actly with the tricks that eyes",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "play. This trickiness varies with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "differences in weather and light-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "ing.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "This writer has seen flying sauc-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "ers over Long Island sound, not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "only this year but in previous",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "years. They were round, bright",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "and moving fast. But they were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "no mystery because they were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "light reflected from the bodies of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "airplanes that soon identified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "themselves by changing course",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "and coming near enough to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "seen distinctly.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "Many descriptions of move-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "ments of the flying saucers fit",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "with the common maneuvers of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "airplanes, singly or in groups.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "Some of the maneuvering report-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "ed, which took saucers out of sight",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "and back into sight again, resem-",
